QuestData.Title: The Battle for the West
QuestData.Description: Our base is barely built and already the Iron Horde sets up defenses against us. Still the plan worked and we fight on two fronts.$b$bI have received word that Durotan has finally breached the western gates as well, but is bogged down in a pitched battle. You should go see the situation for yourself.
QuestData.LogDescription: Go to the Iron Front and speak with Durotan.

Objectives.Objective: Talk to Gargash to fly to the Iron Front
